Calculate USHE Element g_14 (Accepted Credit from Other Sources )

Usage

g_14(input_df = usheUtils::fake_graduation_df, with_intermediates = FALSE)

Arguments

input_df

A Data Frame. Must contain the following data fields: (total_cumulative_credits_attempted_other_sources).

with_intermediates

Boolean: Option to include intermediate calculated fields.

Value

Original data frame, with USHE data element g_14 appended. Will also return appended intermediate calculated fields, if option is set.

Details

USHE Documentation

  • ELEMENT NAME: Accepted Credit from Other Sources

  • FIELD NAME: g_hrs_other

  • FIELD FORMAT: Numeric (4,1)

  • DEFINITION: Hours from AP credit, CLEP test, Language test, Challenge, Military, etc. Hours should all be converted to semester hours.
